desc: Located in Southern California we have a large selection of quality used parts for pre-2000 Mercedes Benz, BMW, Jaguar, AUDI, Volvo and other European cars. Rare and hard to find items at best prices.. Lots of cars in stock. Inventory updated weekly.

layout.text:
Here in Vintage European we love classic European cars from 80`s and 90`s and we strive to offer fellow enthusiasts high quality used parts at affordable prices.
Lots of parts in stock.
Inventory updated weekly.
If you do not see the part that you need - ask us and we might just have it.
